// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚ēö‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ     ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ     ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ
// config by furcom (https://github.com/furcom)

// More settings: https://github.com/davatorium/rofi/blob/next/doc/rofi-theme.5.markdown

@import "./colors.rasi"

* {
  font: "0xProto Nerd Font Mono 18";

  r1: 1em;
  r2: 2em;
  r100: 100%;

  b015: 0.15em;
  b0125: 0.125em;

  s01: 0.1em;
  s02: 0.2em;
  s04: 0.4em;
  s08: 0.8em;
  s16: 1.6em;
  s32: 3.2em;
  s64: 6.4em;
  s128: 12.8em;
  s256: 25.6em;
}

configuration {

  // General setting
  case-sensitive: false;
  cycle: true;
  filter: "";
  icon-theme: "Papirus";
  modi: "";
  normalize-match: true;
  scroll-method: 0;
  show-icons: true;
  steal-focus: true;
  matching: "normal";
  tokenize: true;

  // SSH settings
  parse-hosts: true;
  parse-known-hosts: true;
  ssh-command: "{terminal} -e {ssh-client} {host} [-p {port}]";
  ssh-client: "ssh";

  // Drun settings
  drun { parse-user:   true; parse-system: true; }
  drun-categories: "";
  drun-display-format: "{icon} {name}";
  drun-match-fields: "name,generic,exec,categories,keywords";
  drun-reload-desktop-cache: false;
  drun-show-actions: false;
  drun-url-launcher: "xdg-open";
  drun-use-desktop-cache: false;

  // Run settings
  run-command: "{cmd}";
  run-list-command: "";
  run-shell-command: "{terminal} -e {cmd}";

  // Fallback Icon
  run,drun {
    fallback-icon: "x";
  }

  // Window switcher settings
  //window-command: "wmctrl -i -R {window}";
  window-format: "{w} {c} {t}";
  window-match-fields: "app-id";
  window-thumbnail: false;

  // Combi settings
  //combi-display-format: "{mode} {text}";
  //combi-hide-mode-prefix: false;
  //combi-modi: "window,run";

  // History and Sorting
  disable-history: false;
  max-history-size: 25;
  sorting-method: "normal";

  // Display setting
  display-combi: "ůįēė Combi";
  display-drun: "Ôíá Apps";
  display-filebrowser: "ÔĄē Files";
  display-keys: "ÔāĄ Keys";
  display-run: "ÔĄ† Run";
  display-ssh: "ÔíČ SSH";
  display-window: "Ó≠Ņ Windows";
  display-windowcd: "Ó¨£ Windows CD";

  // Misc setting
  click-to-exit: true;
  // ignored-prefixes: "";
  // pid: "/run/user/1000/rofi.pid";
  sort: false;
  terminal: "rofi-sensible-terminal";
  threads: 0;

  // File browser settings
  filebrowser {
    // directory: "/home";
    directories-first: true;
    sorting-method: "name";
  }

  //Other settings
  timeout { action: "kb-cancel"; delay: 0; }
}

window {
  anchor: center;
  background-color: @background;
  border: @b015;
  border-color: @primary;
  border-radius: @r2;
  location: center;
  padding: @s16;
  height: 45%;
  width: 35%;
}

mainbox {
  children: ["inputbar","listview"];
}

listview {
  border: 0em;
  cycle: true;
  columns: 2;
  dynamic: true;
  expand: true;
  layout: vertical;
  scrollbar: true;
  spacing: @s02;
  reverse: false;
  fixed-columns: false;
  require-input: false;
}

scrollbar {
  border-radius: @r100;
  handle-color: @primary;
  handle-width: 0.3em;
  width: @s08;
  height: @s08;
}

sidebar {
  border-radius: @r1;
  border-color: none;
}

num-filtered-rows {
  expand: false;
  text-color: @foreground;
}

num-rows {
  expand: false;
  text-color: @foreground;
}

textbox-num-sep {
  expand: false;
  str: "/";
  text-color: @foreground;
}

inputbar {
  children: ["entry","mode-switcher"];
  margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;
  text-color: @foreground;
  border: @b0125;
  border-color: @primary;
  border-radius: @r1;
  padding: @s02;
}

entry {
  expand: true;
  background-color: @background-dark;
  cursor: text;
  padding: 0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.2em;
  margin: 0 0 0 0.4em;
  placeholder: "‚ÄąSearch";
  placeholder-color: @primary-dark;
  text-color: @primary;
  vertical-align: center;
}

prompt {
  expand: false;
  padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
  str: "ÔÄā";
  text-color: @background;
  background-color: @primary;
  border-radius: @r1;
  vertical-align: center;
}

textbox-prompt-colon {
  expand: false;
  padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
  str: "ÔÄā";
  text-color: @background;
  background-color: @primary;
  margin: 0 -0.4em 0 0;
  border-radius: @r1;
  vertical-align: center;
}

mode-switcher{
  enabled: true;
  text-color: @background;
  background-color: @primary;
  border-radius: @r1;
  vertical-align: center;
}

button {
  background-color: @background;
  border: @b015;
  border-color: @primary;
  border-radius: @r1;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: @s02;
  text-color: @primary-dark;
  width: 4.5em;
}

button selected {
  background-color: @primary;
  text-color: @background;
}

element {
  border-radius: @r1;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: @s04;
}

element normal.normal { background-color: @background; text-color: @foreground; }
element normal.urgent { background-color: #ff0000; text-color: @foreground; }
element normal.active { background-color: @background; text-color: @foreground; }
element selected.normal { background-color: @primary; text-color: @foreground; }
element selected.urgent { background-color: #770000; text-color: @foreground; }
element selected.active { background-color: @primary; text-color: @foreground; }
element alternate.normal { background-color: @background; text-color: @foreground; }
element alternate.urgent { background-color: #ff0000; text-color: @foreground; }
element alternate.active { background-color: @background; text-color: @foreground; }
element-text { background-color: transparent; cursor: inherit; highlight: inherit; text-color: inherit; }
element-icon { background-color: transparent; size: 1.0000em; cursor: inherit; text-color: inherit; }
